     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<pre>                                                                q2 t1                                       t1      q2 t1                                       t1\n<span class=\"wl-message\">ReplaceRepeated::reps</span>: {s - (t1 + t2) w :> s - (t1 + t2) w, s - ----- - (t1 + t2) w :> s - (t1 + t2) w - q2 --, s + ----- - (t1 + t2) w :> s - (t1 + t2) w + q2 --, Null} is neither a list of replacement rules nor a valid dispatch table, and so cannot be used for replacing.\n                                                                  m                                         m         m                                         m</pre>",
